OOC: Northlight, what's an adress I can use to adress you personally ?

BIC:
Starscream, Cliffjumper thought, as his face soured at the name. He was
trying his best not to create a scene, and make himself look like an
idiot, but he was about to rage. Starscream killed many of his friends,
including Brawn, Ratchet, and Ironhide. He looked away from Redhot,
disgusted, and took a step away.

Firedrill on the otherhand, was fascinated. "Really? You used to be a
Decepticon?" he was taking it all in, with a big smile on his face.
